pick up the squirt bottle on the top shelf to the right
walk to the toilet
put the squirt bottle on the toilet tank top
walk to the shelves with the yellow squirt bottles
pick up the squirt bottle on the top shelf

put the squirt bottle on the toilet tank next to the other squirt bottle

high_descs: Take a step to the left to face the dish rack.
Pick up the yellow spray bottle on the right of the top shelf of the dish rack.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the toilet.
Place the yellow spray bottle on the back of the toilet.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the dish rack.
Pick up the yellow spray bottle on the top shelf of the dish rack.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the toilet.
Place the yellow spray bottle on the back of the toilet beside the first spray bottle.
anns.task_desc: To move two yellow spray bottle from a dish rack to the back of the sink.

high_descs: Walk to the metal shelves in front of you.
Pick up the yellow spray bottle on the right.
Turn around and walk to the toilet.
Put the spray bottle down on the back of the toilet to the left.
Turn around and walk back to the metal shelves.
Pick up the remaining yellow spray bottle on the top shelf.
Turn around and walk back to the toilet.
Put the spray bottle on the back of the toilet to the right of the first spray bottle.
anns.task_desc: To move two spray bottles to the back of the toilet.
